## Development

```bash
git clone https://github.com/bloodbee/jrt.git
cd jrt-python
poetry install --with dev

# run tests
pytest -q
```

---

## Running the CLI from source

```bash
poetry run jrt convert examples/jsons/simple.json --output output.rdf
```

